\end {aligned}
]]></fr:tex>
            <fr:p>The above may be extended to a <fr:link href="jms-003F.xml" title="Wild 1-semi-functor" addr="jms-003F" type="local">wild 1-semi-functor</fr:link> as follows:</fr:p>
