            <fr:anchor>15721</fr:anchor>
            <fr:addr type="user">jms-0037</fr:addr>
            <fr:route>jms-0037.xml</fr:route>
            <fr:title text="Wild category">Wild category</fr:title>
            <fr:taxon>Definition</fr:taxon>
          </fr:frontmatter>
          <fr:mainmatter>
            <fr:p>A <fr:em>wild category</fr:em> is given by the following data:</fr:p>
            <fr:ol><fr:li>a type <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathbf {ob}_{\mathcal {C}}]]></fr:tex>;</fr:li>
  <fr:li>for each <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[A,B:\mathbf {ob}_{\mathcal {C}}]]></fr:tex>, a family of types <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathbf {hom}_{\mathcal {C}}{\mathopen {}\left (A,B\right )\mathclose {}}]]></fr:tex>;</fr:li>
  <fr:li>for each <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[A:\mathbf {ob}_{\mathcal {C}}]]></fr:tex>, an element <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[1_{A} : \mathbf {hom}_{\mathcal {C}}{\mathopen {}\left (A,A\right )\mathclose {}}]]></fr:tex>;</fr:li>
  <fr:li>for each <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[f:\mathbf {hom}_{\mathcal {C}}{\mathopen {}\left (A,B\right )\mathclose {}}]]></fr:tex> and <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[g:\mathbf {hom}_{\mathcal {C}}{\mathopen {}\left (B,C\right )\mathclose {}}]]></fr:tex>, an element <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[{\mathopen {}\left (f;g\right )\mathclose {}} : \mathbf {hom}_{\mathcal {C}}{\mathopen {}\left (A,C\right )\mathclose {}}]]></fr:tex></fr:li>
  <fr:li>for each <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[f:\mathbf {hom}_{\mathcal {C}}{\mathopen {}\left (A,B\right )\mathclose {}}]]></fr:tex>, a identification <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathsf {lunit}_{\mathcal {C}} f : {\mathopen {}\left (1_{A};f\right )\mathclose {}} = f]]></fr:tex> and a identification <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathsf {runit}_{\mathcal {C}} f : {\mathopen {}\left (f;1_{B}\right )\mathclose {}}=f]]></fr:tex>;</fr:li>
  <fr:li>for each <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[f:\mathbf {hom}_{\mathcal {C}}{\mathopen {}\left (A,B\right )\mathclose {}}]]></fr:tex> and <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[g:\mathbf {hom}_{\mathcal {C}}{\mathopen {}\left (B,C\right )\mathclose {}}]]></fr:tex> and <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[h:\mathbf {hom}_{\mathcal {C}}{\mathopen {}\left (C,D\right )\mathclose {}}]]></fr:tex>, a identification <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathsf {assoc}_{\mathcal {C}}\,f\,g\,h : f;{\mathopen {}\left (g;h\right )\mathclose {}} = {\mathopen {}\left (f;g\right )\mathclose {}};h]]></fr:tex>.</fr:li></fr:ol>
          </fr:mainmatter>
        </fr:tree>
